You are in the restaurant in the restaurant car. Outside the windows, the landscape is rushing by.The restaurant can be entered from the lobby to the east of here, and the kitchen is to the west. A sign on the one door going west says "No passengers". In here, there are several guests eating and a waiter moving around. There are 7 tables here, numbered accordingly. Table 7 stand the furthest to the west. Behind a counter stand a bartender, dressed in similar clothes. There are several tables here, but most are of no interest.
