The counter runs a short bit along the southern wall of the restaurang, close to the west end. It is made out of dark and shiny wood. Painted on it is letters, spelling out: "Drinks, 5 $". There is also a smaller text in the local languge: "Trenker, 5 Thal."
it contains a money.
> take money

> take money
