Time passes.
"Dawdling will not be tolerated!"
You practically get dragged away to compartment 14. No one seems to notice. You are practically pushed in.
As soon as you get inside, you feel that something is wrong.
On the floor before you lies the man in the grey suit. There is no blood.
"You just left the recorder? Have you any conception... In any case, it is irrelevant. I've got it right here."
The man who twisted yoru arms earlier, and who just dragged you in, nods towards the seat where the recorder is. Now he is holding a gun in one hand and one of your arms in the other. Once again, he has you in his grip.
"We had a slight disagreement..."
He reaches for the tape recorder.
"...but everything is all right now. Thank you for your cooperation. Good work."
The man in the grey suit is not moving.
"I guess he has had one drink too many. Speaking of which..."
Without looking away from you, he reaches for a glass somewhere.
"Dink it. Cheers."
He puts the glass in your hand and retrieves the recorder from the seat. His gun is aimed right at you.

The compartment looks like yours, only a bit bigger. Also, the carpeting and seat is another color.
You can go southwest or out.
You can see an aging man and a big man.
> drink tall drink

> drink tall drink
Cringing slightly, you still swallow the drink. Something is definitely wrong with the taste.
"Like I said: Cheers."
The man smiles ironically while he leaves, locking you in the compartment behind him. Almost immediately, you get a strange feeling in your stomach.
> move aging man

> move aging man
You manage to move the man slightly. Under him, or perhaps in a pocket, was the key to the compartment. Some people are stupid.
> search aging man

> search aging man
You quickly search the man. The only interesting thing you can find is a piece cut out of a newspaper.
> x newspaper cut-out

> x newspaper cut-out
It is a small piece cut out of a newspaper, containing an advertismen for a motel. There is a pictures of it (it looks quite run-down) as well as the adress. The adress has been underlined.
> unlock door

> unlock door
You unlock the compartment door. The key breaks and is stuck in the lock. You leave it there.
