> enter room 204
You walk into the hotel room.

You are in the hotel room you rented. It is not very big, and not any cleaner. The window is located on the north side of the room, while the exit is to the south. There is not a lot in here, but there is an uncomfortable bed, a small chair and some non-descript hotel room furniture.
You can go south.
Seeing the bed makes you realize how tired you are.
