You lie down on the bed, and instantly begin to fall asleep. Your tired mind drifts away, and you sleep for quite a while.
When you wake up, you find yourself back on the train.
This is a rather nice and clean compartment on a train. The seat has been removed, but you recognize this as one of the compartments you visited earlier. The window is on the northern side of the compartment.
You can go south.
