You are on a street, running north-south a bit east of the station. To the south, you can see a police roadblock. It blocks the street to the west (where the station is), but you could not walk past it without being spotted. The buildings all around you are of no interest. Further to the north, you can see a small parking lot and more of the street.
There is a street vendor here, carrying a tray. It is markes "Kaffee/Coffee 5 Thal."
You can go west, south or north.
