As you walk up to the parking lot, you can see a man wearing a dark grey or black trenchcoat some way to the north of you.
"You there!"
He turns and starts quickly in your direction.
"Stay right there!"

You are standing est of a parking lot, easily accesible through climbing over the low railing to your west. To your east you can see the facade of a concrete building; there is a bookstore at ground level, with big windows. The road you are standing on continues to the north and south of here.
You can go south, east or north.
You can see the man in the trenchcoat closing in on you. He is much faster than you, and you could not avoid him for long out in the open.
