The man enters the bookstore. He dashes towards you, and you couldn't make it out of here while he is here.
> hit man

> hit man
You manage to hit the man, but without force.
The man throws a punch at you, catching you off guard. He hits you in the face and your head is spinning.
> hit man

> hit man
You punch the man right on the jaw, and he almost falls over.
The man kicks at you, and somehow manages to hit despite his condition. It hurts a lot.
> kick man

> kick man
You kick at the man. He tries to twist out of the way, but instead ends up with your foot on his neck. It snaps, and he stops moving. While you have done nothing wrong, you might run into trouble by staying here.
> x dead man

> x dead man
The man in the trenchcoat is dead. There is a bit of blood, but his defining feature is still the black coat. His face in nondescript, and you cannot see anything interesting about him.
